---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components'
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'

import imageLogo from '@svg/w-logo-03-vector-web.svg'
---

<footer class='mt-16 fondo'>
  <div class='mx-auto w-full max-w-screen-xl px-5'>
    <div
      class='-mt-20 mb-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 rounded-xl bg-sky-700 px-6 py-6 md:grid-cols-2 md:px-20 md:py-14 shadow-xl'
    >
      <div>
        <h3 class='max-w-sm text-2xl font-semibold leading-8 text-white md:pr-6'>
          Todas las novedades directo a tu bandeja de entrada. <span class='text-amber-500'
            >Suscríbete al boletín semanal.</span
          >
        </h3>
      </div>
      <form action=''>
        <div class='relative flex flex-col gap-5 rounded-2xl shadow-sm sm:flex-row sm:gap-0'>
          <input
            type='email'
            name='email'
            class='block flex-1 rounded-lg border-2 border-white bg-white px-6 py-5 ps-14 text-sm focus:z-10 focus:border-jungle-green-600 focus:outline-none sm:rounded-s-2xl'
            placeholder='Tu correo electrónico'
          />
          <div class='pointer-events-none absolute start-0 top-5 z-20 flex items-center ps-5 opacity-60 sm:inset-y-0'>
            <Icon name='mail' size={25} class='text-sky-700' />
          </div>
          <button
            type='submit'
            class='items-center justify-center gap-x-2 rounded-lg border border-transparent px-8 py-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400 via-amber-500 to-amber-600 hover:bg-gradient-to-br focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-amber-200 dark:focus:ring-amber-700 text-white sm:rounded-e-2xl'
            >Suscribirme</button
          >
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
    <div class='grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 md:gap-10'>
      <div class='flex flex-col gap-4 items-center md:items-start mb-8'>
        <figure class='text-center'>
          <Image src={imageLogo} alt='Logo de Alejandro Escobar Coaching' width={200} height={200} loading='lazy' />
        </figure>
      </div>
      <div>
        <ul class='leading-10 text-center md:text-left'>
          <li>
            <a href='#' class='text-lg font-light text-white opacity-75 transition hover:opacity-100'>Sobre mi</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href='#' class='text-lg font-light text-white opacity-75 transition hover:opacity-100'>Metodologia</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href='#' class='text-lg font-light text-white opacity-75 transition hover:opacity-100'>Servicios</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href='#' class='text-lg font-light text-white opacity-75 transition hover:opacity-100'>Testimonios</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <ul class='leading-10 text-center md:text-left'>
          <li>
            <a href='#' class='text-lg font-light text-white opacity-75 transition hover:opacity-100'>LinkedIn</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href='#' class='text-lg font-light text-white opacity-75 transition hover:opacity-100'>Zaask</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href='#' class='text-lg font-light text-white opacity-75 transition hover:opacity-100'
              >WhatsApp Bussines</a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <ul class='leading-10 text-center md:text-left'>
          <li>
            <a href='#' class='text-lg font-light text-white opacity-75 transition hover:opacity-100'>Facebook</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href='#' class='text-lg font-light text-white opacity-75 transition hover:opacity-100'>X</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href='#' class='text-lg font-light text-white opacity-75 transition hover:opacity-100'>Instagram</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href='#' class='text-lg font-light text-white opacity-75 transition hover:opacity-100'>Threads</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class='mt-16 flex flex-col gap-2 border-t border-white border-opacity-20 py-10 text-center md:flex-row md:justify-between md:text-start'
    >
      <p class='font-light text-white opacity-75'>© 2024 Alejandro Escobar. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
      <p class='font-light text-white opacity-75'>
        Desarrollado por <a href='#' class='decoration-amber-500 decoration-double underline'>Manuel Denis Developer.</a
        >
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
